    "name": "Eye: The Journey",
    "steam_appid": 3276910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事与氛围</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eye: The Journey</strong> 延续了在 <strong>Sqube: The Beginning</strong> 中引入的神秘世界。在这款游戏中，过去的一些未解之谜将得到解答，而新的谜题和未知等待着玩家。我们的主角置身于一个更加复杂和危险的环境中，试图揭示自己的起源以及未来的命运。随着玩家的推进，关于世界的更多信息将被揭示，但故事的神秘感将一直持续到最后。叙事并非通过对话，而是通过氛围和环境来讲述，让玩家能够完全沉浸在探索过程中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/ea00f610a7b9926fc58698354ad8c7dc.poster.avif?t=1736424859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/ea00f610a7b9926fc58698354ad8c7dc.webm?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/ea00f610a7b9926fc58698354ad8c7dc.mp4?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于经典的弹跳球机制，<strong>Eye: The Journey</strong> 提供了独特的平台游戏体验。玩家控制一个弹跳的球，穿越平台并与环境互动。在某些关卡中，球可以使用激光移动物体或获得新的能力，例如打破墙壁以进入以前无法到达的区域。每一个新能力都能让玩家解决不同的谜题，并在游戏中推进。随着游戏的进行，谜题变得越来越复杂，通过创造性的机制挑战玩家的智慧和策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5a9614613e3fe2ff8ef6e7e65606f543.poster.avif?t=1736424859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5a9614613e3fe2ff8ef6e7e65606f543.webm?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5a9614613e3fe2ff8ef6e7e65606f543.mp4?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eye: The Journey</strong> 采用 3D 横版卷轴格式，呈现了一个充满深度和细节的世界。尽管游戏使用 3D 模型，但游戏玩法以侧面视角展开，专注于平台元素，同时允许玩家探索一个广阔的世界。每个关卡都有其独特的配色方案，创造出不同的氛围——从阴暗威胁的环境到充满霓虹光亮的关卡。原创且富有创意的关卡设计打破了传统的平台游戏模式，给玩家带来新颖且令人兴奋的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/b2b8e57d17dbcf5b7721be0e2d7673f7.poster.avif?t=1736424859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/b2b8e57d17dbcf5b7721be0e2d7673f7.webm?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/b2b8e57d17dbcf5b7721be0e2d7673f7.mp4?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制简单但流畅；玩家只需控制一个弹跳球，但这种简单性并不会影响游戏的深度。凭借跳跃、使用激光和利用新获得的能力来解决谜题等直观的机制，玩家会完全沉浸在游戏体验中。控制响应迅速且精确，让玩家感受到完全的控制感，使解谜过程更加令人满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5d3a8a1f4377174d181d61ca069da600.poster.avif?t=1736424859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5d3a8a1f4377174d181d61ca069da600.webm?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276910/extras/5d3a8a1f4377174d181d61ca069da600.mp4?t=1736424859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
